c: 14
v: 9
t: "Have you not heard of those before you — of the people of Noah and AAad and Thamood, and those after them? None knows them but Allah. Their Messengers came to them with clear signs. And they thrust their hands into their mouths in astonishment while witnessing those signs, but said, \"We do not believe in the Message that you are sent with, and we are indeed utterly in doubt about what you invite us to"